{"tid":1668863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民意研究所「我們香港人」計劃","createTime":"2019-10-22T08:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T10:38:46.000Z","uid":48667,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"02a94a265d6ea6595f566220073e8fb06138a86b","tid":1668863,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:29:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/wehkers-index\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fwehkers-index&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=6a6cbebe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/wehkers-index</a><br />\n<br />\n連登好似無人提過呢樣野, <br />\n上次17號開記招講施政報告既民意調查個陣, <br />\n已經有講過呢個計劃<br />\n<br />\n咁呢個計劃到底有咩咁把炮呢?<br />\n其中一個就係只要你係民研意見群組既成員, 都可以提交提問既題目<br />\n條題目就有機會成為研究題目進行滾動調查<br />\n個計劃就今日正式開波, 但已經進行左五條先導計劃<br />\n結果就今日公布左, 可以去呢條link 到睇返<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CzfUPVjIWqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCzfUPVjIWqs&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=a3acd3a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CzfUPVjIWqs</a><br />\n<br />\n咁邊個決定條題目應唔應該問呢? <br />\n都會係民研意見群組既成員<br />\n你係可以就住每一條題目投票<br />\n所以成個計劃都可以話係香港人主導<br />\n<br />\n以上兩樣野, 都可以去最頂個條link, 碌到最底<br />\n&quot;意見題目提交平台&quot; 同埋&quot;意見題目表決平台&quot;可以見到<br />\n至於意見群組既成員, 只要係佢個website 右上角&quot;HKPOP Panel&quot; 登記就可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然啦, 做民調係要錢既, 所以佢都新開左個眾籌計劃, <br />\n希望大家除左幫眾志, 大專學界籌錢之後, 都唔好唔記得民意研究所呢啲咁重要既機構<br />\n<br />\n另外想講既就係「公民社會贊助計劃」<br />\n只要一次性捐$12000 就可以問一條問題,<br />\n詳情可以睇下呢條link 最底<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/subscription\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fsubscription&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=7bb1c87b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/subscription</a><br />\n<br />\n而黎緊由呢個贊助計劃入面提出, 將會問既問題,<br />\n就係&quot;香港市民是否贊成港獨?&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bfmMt6wb5Oo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbfmMt6wb5Oo&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=8abc5101\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bfmMt6wb5Oo</a><br />\n大概18:20 左右開始聽啦<br />\n到時收到記得踴躍發表意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好忽視呢啲民意調查既計劃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5154949c177d16825b763594d882650b399f75","tid":1668863,"uid":48667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:29:56.000Z","msg":"有講錯既話請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78143ec6097ae83c62f35d56cada26451a9042c","tid":1668863,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:32:16.000Z","msg":"幫幫手推下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99e7436fa24ecb6ab0a73d7ad70fa5690bf4972","tid":1668863,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccf8c1aacc5a13945c1248e8d9831407301c5c3","tid":1668863,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1248e9f95d35fb67910ed98db6750c2809f16d0d","tid":1668863,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f533171689a156f62eb854fa99a171a6570f39","tid":1668863,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完記得幫下鍾庭耀教授"},{"pid":"575fe5a038e1e3cca41ebb2ab782f0a629042b6e","tid":1668863,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets